{"tid":975263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果CEO庫克去年加薪22％ 達1570萬美元","createTime":"2019-01-09T13:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T14:07:38.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4005b54d191b8e1d658f60db91a261b0afb8f46a","tid":975263,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T13:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2019/01/09/phpkLJTGZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F01%2F09%2FphpkLJTGZ.jpg&h=c8d3385a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖說：蘋果執行長庫克2018年共拿到基本薪資及獎金1570萬美元，約是蘋果一般員工的283倍。（歐新社檔案照）<br />\n<br />\n〔編譯王惠慧／綜合報導〕蘋果日前因iPhone銷售疲軟調降財測，但上個財年仍達先前設定的目標；根據蘋果週二向美國證券交易委員會（SEC）申報的文件顯示，蘋果執行長庫克去年領到基本薪資連同獎金共1570萬美元（約台幣4.84億），約是蘋果一般員工的283倍，且較前年增加22%。<br />\n<br />\n雖然蘋果最近表現不佳，丟下降財測的震撼彈，但截至去年9月的2018財年，蘋果達成了年度財務目標；庫克的獎金與蘋果營收和營業利益目標有關，2項目標均較去年數字增加16%。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》報導，蘋果2018財年表現超出董事會設定的目標，庫克的薪水連續第2年上升，其中包含現金獎勵1200萬美元；根據申報文件，連同薪資及現金獎勵，庫克去年共收到約1570萬美元薪酬，年增22%。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果員工在同年度的年薪中位數為5.54萬美元（約台幣170.8萬），庫克的年薪約是蘋果一般員工的283倍；除了薪資及獎金之外，庫克還從10年股票獎勵計畫中獲得價值1.21億美元的股票，總計庫克在2018財年收入累計達1.36億美元（約台幣41.9億）。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，蘋果包含零售店員工的一般員工年薪中位數為5.54萬美元，明顯低於臉書一般員工年薪中位數24.04萬美元（約台幣741萬）、Google母公司Alphabet的19.7萬美元（約台幣607萬）；亞馬遜和蘋果一樣，因為擁有大量零倉儲人員，年薪中位數約落在3萬美元（約台幣92.5萬）。<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2666395\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2666395&d=4Sab%2FE2bwNSfTzLaAb%2BW4BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=662bb574\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2666395&h=3b9da886\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2666395</a>"},{"pid":"c4fb7ddd93a0beddbb2d6eb84fb08f288c8aa135","tid":975263,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T13:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4adbfd442761c6120b981bcf92eb01e67c9581a3","tid":975263,"uid":134474,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T13:24:31.000Z","msg":"同香港啲狗官一樣，冇料到就加人工"},{"pid":"e9ae00f9d61bb2bc9cbb67c05470e85f21487a2a","tid":975263,"uid":134474,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T13:24:57.000Z","msg":"肥上瘦下"},{"pid":"a974adbe1219777e832f0a3bef674db73dcc52be","tid":975263,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T13:25:27.000Z","msg":"正 加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa32fc16f59dc8d6f7385b3803ba46d42f29be3","tid":975263,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T13:28:52.000Z","msg":"一皮買電話不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbcea020e134e179a85fa3d80f4ea6431b4426ba","tid":975263,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T13:39:43.000Z","msg":"極唔情願俾錢去養呢條契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f74fc4958158dc0214420072f952f638e1fe5f","tid":975263,"uid":42760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T13:45:15.000Z","msg":"史上最高人工基佬"},{"pid":"866ce6cae604757ba57d9d68d8dbc458bfa7f652","tid":975263,"uid":3773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T14:07:38.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死基廚"}]}